## What is urchinbot?

A Chrome extension that injects an AI-powered overlay on any webpage. It can see your page, answer questions, build entire websites, scan Solana tokens, and help deploy memecoins on Pump.fun â€” all from a floating panel in your browser.

### Features

- **Ask** â€” Chat with an AI agent that can see your current page, selected text, tweets, and uploaded files
- **Build** â€” Generate full static websites (HTML/CSS/JS) from a text description, preview inline, download as ZIP, or deploy to Netlify instantly
- **Deploy** â€” Prepare Pump.fun launch packets, auto-fill pump.fun/create with token info + image upload
- **Scan** â€” Analyze any Solana token mint for top holder concentration, fresh wallet flags, and rug signals
- **Edit via Chat** â€” Tell the bot "change the background to dark purple" and it edits your built site in place
- **Grab Page Images** â€” Pull images from any webpage to use in your builds or deploys
- **Right-click Context Menu** â€” Send selected text, links, or images directly to urchinbot
- **Netlify Deploy** â€” One-click deploy any generated site to a live `.netlify.app` URL

---

## Installation

1. **Download or clone** this repo
2. Open Chrome and go to `chrome://extensions`
3. Enable **Developer mode** (toggle in the top right)
4. Click **Load unpacked**
5. Select the `urchinbot-extension` folder
6. Pin the extension from the puzzle piece menu in your toolbar

---

## Setup â€” API Keys

Click the urchinbot icon in your toolbar, then click **Settings** (or right-click the icon â†’ Options).

### LLM Provider (required)

This powers all AI features â€” chat, site building, token analysis summaries.

| Provider | How to get a key | Model suggestion |
|---|---|---|
| **OpenAI** | [platform.openai.com/api-keys](https://platform.openai.com/api-keys) | `gpt-4o-mini` (fast + cheap) or `gpt-4o` (better sites) |
| **Anthropic** | [console.anthropic.com](https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys) | `claude-sonnet-4-20250514` |
| **OpenAI Compatible** | Any provider with an OpenAI-compatible API (Groq, Together, local Ollama, etc.) | Set the base URL + model name |

**Steps:**
1. Pick your provider from the dropdown
2. Paste your API key
3. Enter the model name (or leave default)
4. If using OpenAI Compatible, enter the base URL (e.g., `http://localhost:11434/v1/chat/completions` for Ollama)
5. Click **Save**

### Solana RPC (optional â€” for token scanning)

Required only if you want to use the Scan tab to analyze Solana tokens.

| Provider | How to get | Free tier |
|---|---|---|
| **Helius** | [helius.dev](https://www.helius.dev/) | 100k requests/day free |
| **QuickNode** | [quicknode.com](https://www.quicknode.com/) | Limited free tier |
| **Public RPC** | `https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com` | Rate limited, not recommended |

**Steps:**
1. Sign up at Helius (recommended) and copy your RPC URL
2. Paste it in the **Solana RPC URL** field
3. Click **Save**

### Netlify (optional â€” for instant web deploy)

Required only if you want to deploy built sites to the web with one click.

**Steps:**
1. Go to [app.netlify.com/user/applications#personal-access-tokens](https://app.netlify.com/user/applications#personal-access-tokens)
2. Click **New access token**, name it "urchinbot"
3. Copy the token (it only shows once)
4. Paste it in the **Netlify Personal Access Token** field
5. Click **Save**

---

## Usage

### Quick Start

1. Click the urchinbot icon â†’ click **Ask** (or any tab bubble)
2. The overlay panel appears on the page
3. Type a question or command in the chat

### Ask Tab (AI Chat)

- Ask anything â€” the bot sees your current page URL, title, and visible text
- Upload files/images with the ðŸ“Ž button
- Grab images from the page with the ðŸ–¼ button
- Build sites: *"build me a crypto portfolio landing page with dark theme"*
- Edit sites: *"make the header gradient purple to teal"*
- Scan tokens: *"scan this token"* (when viewing a page with Solana mints)
- Deploy tokens: *"deploy a token called DogWifHat"* (prepares the launch packet)

### Build Tab

- Describe the site you want
- Click **Build Site** â€” generates index.html, styles.css, app.js
- **Preview** â€” renders the site in an iframe
- **Download ZIP** â€” saves the project locally
- **Deploy to Netlify** â€” pushes it live instantly

### Deploy Tab

- Fill in token name, symbol, description
- Upload a token image
- **Generate Launch Packet** â€” AI creates the full launch plan
- **Open & Autofill Pump.fun** â€” opens pump.fun/create and fills all fields + uploads your image
- **Deploy Token Landing Page** â€” creates and deploys a token website to Netlify

### Scan Tab

- Paste a Solana mint address
- See top 10 holders, concentration %, fresh wallet flags
- Links to Solscan for deeper analysis

### Right-Click Menu

- **Select text** â†’ right-click â†’ "Send selection to urchinbot"
- **Right-click a link** â†’ "Send link to urchinbot"
- **Right-click an image** â†’ "Send image to urchinbot"
- **Right-click page** â†’ "Capture current page"

### Keyboard Shortcuts

- `Ctrl+Shift+U` â€” Toggle the overlay panel
- `Escape` â€” Close the overlay

