---

## Security Notes

- **Local-first** â€” All API keys are stored in `chrome.storage.local` on your machine. Nothing is sent to any server except the LLM provider you configure.
- **No custodial keys** â€” urchinbot never touches your wallet private keys. Pump.fun deploys are done by auto-filling the form â€” you confirm and sign the transaction yourself.
- **No tracking** â€” Zero analytics, zero telemetry, zero data collection.

---

## Disclaimers

- urchinbot is a tool for research and experimentation. It does not provide financial advice.
- Memecoins are extremely risky. DYOR (Do Your Own Research).
- The Pump.fun integration assists with form filling only. You are responsible for reviewing and confirming all transactions.
- Sites generated by the AI should be reviewed before deploying to production.

